adamw优化器那里合并单元格，三列合并为一行

以下是修改后的代码，将 AdamW 优化器那一行的三列合并为一个单元格：

```latex
\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \setlength{\tabcolsep}{3pt}
    \caption{
        \textbf{Key hyperparameters of different training stages.}
    }
    \resizebox{0.6\textwidth}{!}{
\begin{tabular}{lccc}
\hline
\textbf{Training Stage}  & \textbf{SFT (stage 1)} & \textbf{SFT (stage 2)} & \textbf{RL} \\ \hline
Optimizer                & \multicolumn{3}{c}{AdamW~\cite{adamw}}                  \\
Learning rate            & 1e-5                   & 1e-5                   &     1e-6        \\
Learning rate scheduler  & cosine                 & cosine                 &     constant        \\
Global batch size               & 256                    & 256                    &   32          \\
Training epochs          & 1                      &1                       & -           \\
Training steps           & 1644                   & 599                    &         400    \\
Max sequence length               & 40000                  & 40000                  &       34816      \\
Max visual tokens & 16384                  & 16384                  &    32768         \\
Max frames       & 768                    & 768                    &      768       \\
GPUs           & 32                     & 32                     &    32         \\ \hline
\end{tabular}
    }
    \label{tab:train_hyperparams}
    % \vspace{-10pt}
\end{table}
```

**主要修改：**
- 将 `Optimizer` 行改为：`& \multicolumn{3}{c}{AdamW~\cite{adamw}} \\`
- 使用 `\multicolumn{3}{c}{...}` 将后面三列合并为一个居中的单元格
